# autoagents workflow

When editing files under `autoagents/` or executing agent steps:

## Task filenames

`<STATUS>-<issue>-<YYYYMMDD>-<HHMM>-<slug>.md`, see `autoagents/TASKS-README.md`.

## Before git-changing steps

```bash
./scripts/git-sync-main.sh
```

## Site version (footer)

**`package.json`** `version` is shown in the site footer. **Every** coder task (FEAT/NEW → UNTESTED) must run **`./scripts/bump-patch-version.sh`** once before renaming to **UNTESTED-** (patch +1). Committer verifies the bump is in the diff.

Branch: **`main`**. Remote: **AMVARA-CONSULTING/km0-web**.

## Agent roles

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `001-gh-reviewer.md` | GH issues → FEAT tasks; Docker incidents → NEW |
| `010-feature-coder.md` | FEAT → WIP → UNTESTED |
| `002-coder/CODER.md` | NEW/WIP → UNTESTED |
| `020-test.md` | UNTESTED → TESTING → CLOSED or WIP |
| `030-closing-reviewer.md` | CLOSED → done/ archive |
| `040-committer.md` | Commit on main |

## Loop

```bash
./autoagents/autoagents-loop.sh [001|feat|coder|tester|closing-review|committer]
```

Uses **cursor-agent** with prompt file body + loop message (`--yolo --print --trust --workspace` repo root). Requires `gh` auth (`./scripts/setup-autoagents-gh.sh`).

## Scope

- Edit product files only in coder/tester roles (`src/`, `astro.config.mjs`, `docs/`).
- 001/030 touch only `autoagents/` task files.
- Never commit `.env`, tokens, or secrets.

## Archive closed tasks

```bash
./scripts/move-agent-task-to-done.sh autoagents/tasks/CLOSED-<N>-<date>-<slug>.md
```
